                        There are two important morals here. First, REST-based SOA is alive      and well, and offers straightforward solutions to many of the      knottier problems that Web Services-based SOA has suffered from. But      even more importantly, the success the USCG has achieved shows that      any architectural approach is nothing more than a loose collection of best practices.<br />
